Description: Spotlight-style Konsole tab finder
 A system tray app with a spotlight-style search window for quickly
 finding and switching between Konsole tabs. Searches by tab title
 and running command (useful for SSH sessions). Works on Wayland
 via KWin D-Bus scripting.
